# Clienta AI — Project Context

**Agent instruction:** This rule is the **primary source** for project layout, architecture, APIs, and conventions. Answer questions about the project from this rule. **Do not run codebase_search or exploratory reads** for general "how does X work?" or "where is Y?" — the answers are below. Only open or read specific files when the user explicitly asks to **edit** a file or when you need a line-level detail not listed here (e.g. exact implementation of a function).

