## What This Is

Multi-tenant SaaS CRM with AI features for small businesses (restaurants, retail, bars). Named **Clienta AI**.

- **Core CRM:** Inventory, transactions, purchase orders, contacts, messages
- **AI:** Business insights (inventory, revenue, reorder suggestions) via Google Gemini
- **Messaging:** WhatsApp via Meta Cloud API + n8n AI agent
- **Payments:** Square (in-store and online)
- **Multi-tenant:** Tenant-scoped data and roles (owner, manager, staff)

